Yeah I know, I'm looking at it abit as shitting on alot of isekai tropes I know, whatever the writer meant to or not (Such as the Isekai Heroine being completely useless, yet still the catalyst that started a fucking war over her! Funny part with the Hero is "how many Female lead Isekai do you know where the male lead's mental state and personality is all over the place!" except here the story makes no attempts to excuse his insanity, he's not a good person!) But good god the Stockholm/Lima is all over the place with them (Would find it funny if the Heroine's purpose WAS to cause these's events to happen simply by BEING there! Meaning anyone could have been picked, she was chosen cause the MC would ONLY be attracted to her if she fit his "sister/mom" description, but is weak willed enough for him to manipulate her into loving him!) Would love to see a gender bended version of this couple some day (not them per say, more the GENDER'S of the one in their positions!)
The plot is actually interesting enough.
